                                    atLeast="2.5"
                                    atMost="9.5"/>
                                <p>s. The lettering varies in height from 2.5 to 6.5 cm in lines
                                    1-11, reaching 9.5 cm in line 12. The Latin text bears traces of
                                    red paint</p>
                            </handNote>
