            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>To the Emperors Caesars, brothers Gaius Valerius Diocletian and Marcus Aurelius
                    Valerius Maximianus, pious, fortunate and invincible Augusti. From Ashqelon,
                    three miles.</p>
